#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn17.6"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn17.6:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 17 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 17 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.6:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga "
msgstr "1. The First Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 6. Asanisutta → asanivicakkasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn17.6:0.3"
msgid "6. Asanisutta "
msgstr "6. A Bolt of Lightning "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn17.6:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.6:1.2"
msgid "“Dāruṇo, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe … adhigamāya. "
msgstr "“Possessions, honor, and popularity are brutal … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: sekhaṃ → sekhaṃ (s1-3, km) | taṃ sekhaṃ (pts1-2, mr) | km sekhaṃ (?)
#. VAR: anupāpuṇātu → anupāpuṇāti (pts1-2, mr)
msgctxt "sn17.6:1.3"
msgid "Kaṃ, bhikkhave, asanivicakkaṃ āgacchatu, sekhaṃ appattamānasaṃ lābhasakkārasiloko anupāpuṇātu. "
msgstr "Who should be struck by lightning? A trainee who comes into possessions, honor, and popularity before they achieve their heart’s desire. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn17.6:2.1"
msgid "Asanivicakkanti kho, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasilokassetaṃ adhivacanaṃ. "
msgstr "‘Lightning strike’ is a term for possessions, honor, and popularity. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.6:2.2"
msgid "Evaṃ dāruṇo kho, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe … "
msgstr "So brutal are possessions, honor, and popularity. …” "

msgctxt "sn17.6:2.3"
msgid "evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn17.6:2.4"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
